Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.32,0:00:06.41,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}確かな想いを伝えたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.85,0:00:18.23,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}戻らない時間に溺れぬように
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.62,0:00:21.97,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}今を抱きしめよう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.12,0:00:28.85,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}その微笑みを行ったり来たり　そばにいたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.06,0:00:36.56,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}この手を伸ばす　先には何が待ってるんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.78,0:00:42.69,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}終わらない物語の向こう　飛び立て
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.93,0:00:47.50,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}本当の気持ちでたどり着く場所へと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.74,0:00:51.49,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心の翼を広げて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.79,0:00:58.50,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}廻りゆくメッセージ　幸せは胸にあるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.58,0:01:02.10,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あと少しの勇気　涙も必要なの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.29,0:01:06.32,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}強くなれるチャンスかもね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.45,0:01:12.92,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}温もりのリフレイン　この大切をずっと守りたい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.01,0:01:16.69,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心を重ねてく　絆を感じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.80,0:01:20.59,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}誰も一人じゃないんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.85,0:01:29.65,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}同じ空の下　確かな想いを伝えたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.32,0:00:06.41,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}这份真情实感　好想将它传递
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.85,0:00:18.23,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}为了不沉溺于一去不返的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.62,0:00:21.97,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}紧紧拥抱今天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.12,0:00:28.85,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}深陷于那微笑之中　好想相伴在你的左右
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.06,0:00:36.56,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}伸出手　前方应该有什么正等待着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.78,0:00:42.69,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}朝着那未完结的故事　飞奔而去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.93,0:00:47.50,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}怀着一颗真诚的心向着那千难万险之地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.74,0:00:51.49,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}张开心灵的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.79,0:00:58.50,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}循环传递着一个讯息　幸福就存于这胸中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.58,0:01:02.10,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}接下来的少许勇气　尽管须以眼泪相佐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.29,0:01:06.32,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}但这或许正是变强的契机
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.45,0:01:12.92,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}温暖的迭句　想要永远将这份珍重守护
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.01,0:01:16.69,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}彼此心绪交织　感受着这其中的羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.80,0:01:20.59,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}所以说没有人是孤身只影的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.85,0:01:29.65,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}同一片蓝天下　好想将这份真情实感传递
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.03,0:00:00.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------ed--------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.60,0:22:19.60,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心の奥集めた　今日の光を持って
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.25,0:22:28.39,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}飛び込んだ未知の先　何が待ってるのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.68,0:22:37.73,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}未来への共鳴　想い出に重ねれば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.93,0:22:46.77,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}勇気になる　強さになる　一人じゃないから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.96,0:22:49.08,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}（聴かせて）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.17,0:22:57.70,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}明日もきっと会えるね　本当の笑顔で行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.89,0:23:06.58,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}夢見る夜明けを　一緒に迎えたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.75,0:23:15.76,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}無限の時間よりも　瞬間を駆け抜けよう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.01,0:23:26.96,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}その夢の声いつか聴かせてね　信じてく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.60,0:22:19.60,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}怀揣着内心深处收集好了的今天的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.25,0:22:28.39,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}跃入未知的前方　那里有什么正等待着我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.68,0:22:37.73,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}若是与未来共鸣　不断忆起今天的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.93,0:22:46.77,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}就会生出勇气　就能变得坚强　也就不再是独自一人了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.96,0:22:49.08,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}（让你倾听）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.17,0:22:57.70,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}明天也一定会与你相遇　我会带着真诚的笑容前去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.89,0:23:06.58,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}好想和你一起迎接梦想中的黎明
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.75,0:23:15.76,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}与其坐拥这无限的时刻　倒不如追赶那绚烂的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.01,0:23:26.96,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}相信我　总有一天会让你倾听那梦中的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.03,0:00:00.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------正文--------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.49,0:01:37.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚吃火锅哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.52,0:01:38.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.09,0:01:39.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.24,0:01:40.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不知怎么回事  
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.22,0:01:43.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天肉卖的特别便宜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.26,0:01:47.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.57,0:01:50.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像个白痴一样更兴奋一点儿如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.89,0:02:04.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就先开吃啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.99,0:02:06.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛啊你  这么突然！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.16,0:02:09.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！别专挑肉吃啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.39,0:02:11.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那本来就是我的肉啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.96,0:02:14.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦好啦  肉还好多呢  别吵架啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.88,0:02:19.83,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}第9碗  难以掩饰了吧？阿珍的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.54,0:02:33.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.24,0:02:42.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我突然觉得自己好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.32,0:02:50.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就不能好好听我说话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.61,0:02:52.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.57,0:02:57.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像有超能力了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.48,0:03:02.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.20,0:03:06.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天是炸虾  今天是火锅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.87,0:03:09.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚饭吃什么我全都梦到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.63,0:03:11.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是预知梦啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.33,0:03:14.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.98,0:03:18.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不相信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.98,0:03:22.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是…但你堂堂正正地说些过去的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.41,0:03:24.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后再说这是预知谁信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.02,0:03:30.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  我说对了明天晚饭吃什么  你会相信吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.70,0:03:33.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊  你说对了我就信
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.32,0:03:36.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就今晚  等我梦见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.58,0:04:07.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰冷的身体温暖起来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.96,0:04:09.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也进来泡吧  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.85,0:04:12.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在吃什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.56,0:04:15.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈  夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.29,0:04:19.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在比较忙  
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.11,0:04:22.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事请在提示音后留言
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.68,0:04:25.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是女孩子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.62,0:04:28.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在旁边哦  在便利店旁边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.99,0:04:35.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈  这都怪你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.99,0:04:41.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那红色的棒子…是什么玩意？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.44,0:04:43.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡萝卜？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.31,0:04:50.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么阿珍会…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.03,0:04:53.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  不管了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.89,0:04:58.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  阿真那家伙心里到底怎么想的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.45,0:05:04.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然一直说讨厌穿女装  但看似乐在其中啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.79,0:05:06.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用管他也行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.42,0:05:13.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改天问问他本人吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.71,0:05:22.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢  那什么预知梦怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.23,0:05:24.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很微妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.47,0:05:28.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我总算是记得点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.94,0:05:30.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.41,0:05:32.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒也不是说不出来啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.34,0:05:36.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼！我就知道会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.54,0:05:37.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预知梦个头啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.46,0:05:39.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我等一下  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.64,0:05:41.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.66,0:05:43.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有重要的事跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.65,0:05:46.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如说  内田很讨厌吃年糕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.09,0:05:48.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？突然说什么啊  
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.96,0:05:50.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内田还是吃年糕的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.91,0:05:52.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦  听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.52,0:05:54.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们假设内田讨厌吃年糕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.70,0:05:59.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让内田不断吃她讨厌的年糕的过程中渐渐喜欢上了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.74,0:06:01.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这可能吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.67,0:06:04.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样  会更讨厌年糕的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.37,0:06:06.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.78,0:06:10.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  看你用什么方法让她吃了  也不是没可能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.20,0:06:16.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受到身边的人影响  人也会改变嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.02,0:06:18.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能变好也能变坏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.64,0:06:20.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说自己会做什么预知梦的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.16,0:06:22.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是身边的人一直无视她  
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.99,0:06:25.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间久了也就不会再提了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.04,0:06:28.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这跟那是两码事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.41,0:06:34.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉～预知梦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.52,0:06:37.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  突然就这么说  吓我一跳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.05,0:06:41.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就觉得今天少了点儿东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.01,0:06:44.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天保坂学长请假了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.39,0:06:45.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.59,0:06:46.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.54,0:06:48.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.90,0:06:50.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的没什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.47,0:06:51.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.92,0:06:54.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  请问有事吗  老师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.93,0:06:57.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能到升学指导室来一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.89,0:06:59.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在…吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.36,0:07:03.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南同学  我想跟你谈的其实是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.27,0:07:06.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道交换留学生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.08,0:07:07.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.17,0:07:13.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望成绩优秀的你能作为我们学校的代表过去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.68,0:07:15.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？但是…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.27,0:07:19.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然可能有很多不便  但这是个机会哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.32,0:07:24.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁着年轻好好见识一下这广阔的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.76,0:07:26.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接触各种各样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.69,0:07:29.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该会对你有所帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.07,0:07:48.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别无视眼前正在犯愁的朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.27,0:07:51.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来你有烦恼啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.08,0:07:55.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样才能准确地记住自己做过的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.11,0:07:57.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说点儿好办法来听听
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.08,0:07:59.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.47,0:08:03.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一醒就记下来怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.45,0:08:06.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能行！这怎么做得到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.53,0:08:08.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～问了白问
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.61,0:08:10.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就别问啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.47,0:08:14.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.05,0:08:16.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多符合夏奈的个性啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.86,0:08:17.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.22,0:08:20.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得就是在说梦话罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.52,0:08:25.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.69,0:08:26.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…没事儿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.54,0:08:34.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去倒垃圾  
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.99,0:08:37.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这段时间你要打扫好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.57,0:08:38.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.85,0:08:41.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋变了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.23,0:08:43.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.17,0:08:44.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？哪里变了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.79,0:08:47.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话变多了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.04,0:08:51.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？我主动搭话的时候她总是无视啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.07,0:08:53.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者说是无视我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.67,0:08:57.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋她以前不喜欢跟别人有过多接触呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.48,0:09:00.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿真你也变了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.47,0:09:02.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经完全是个伪娘了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.46,0:09:03.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.78,0:09:04.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.20,0:09:08.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是夏奈非要我穿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.21,0:09:11.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外加遗传爸爸的服务精神使然
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.45,0:09:11.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.09,0:09:13.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说真的！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.66,0:09:18.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天要去千秋家写作业  羡慕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.39,0:09:22.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈有没有叫阿珍一起去？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.53,0:09:24.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.64,0:09:26.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作业怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.17,0:09:29.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么  你也要来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.77,0:09:33.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…今天我也可以一起去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.96,0:09:35.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.15,0:09:38.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  快进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.96,0:09:39.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.82,0:09:40.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.94,0:09:45.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.73,0:09:47.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.41,0:09:49.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  吉野  内田也来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.18,0:09:53.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.49,0:09:54.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁啊这是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.83,0:09:58.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你再怎么欺负他也不会觉得有趣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.31,0:10:00.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.83,0:10:02.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？阿真…？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.75,0:10:04.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得到千秋的同意了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.61,0:10:06.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天可以堂堂正正的来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.03,0:10:08.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.63,0:10:10.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会再受夏奈你的摆布了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.31,0:10:15.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从妈妈那遗传的男子气概是绝不允许那种行为的！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.21,0:10:19.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没同意啊  这可是我家！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.03,0:10:20.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.29,0:10:30.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然刚到没多久  你还是赶紧滚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.93,0:10:32.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.78,0:10:34.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轮不到你有异议！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.91,0:10:49.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿真
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.86,0:10:54.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈让我把这个给你…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.76,0:11:00.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.39,0:11:02.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  是阿珍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.33,0:11:04.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是朝气十足啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.98,0:11:07.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  我也不明白是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.68,0:11:24.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三号舰严重受损  我军阵形已经崩溃了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.53,0:11:28.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  出动新型机  无论如何要守住这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.91,0:11:32.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Class Copper已做好离舰准备  舰桥请指示！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.49,0:11:33.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.99,0:11:35.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  夏奈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.31,0:11:37.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.87,0:11:38.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.56,0:11:40.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的变装完美吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.75,0:11:41.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.82,0:11:44.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说  我问这身变装完美吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.94,0:11:47.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛  还算是可以啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.63,0:11:49.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没被千秋揭穿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.77,0:11:51.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内田知道我的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.75,0:11:56.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那吉野呢  难不成已经被她发现了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.21,0:11:58.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.65,0:11:59.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.44,0:12:00.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你慌个什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.23,0:12:03.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愿意被揭穿的话就别干了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.49,0:12:04.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.23,0:12:08.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这样好像是我逼着你穿女装似的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.20,0:12:10.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实你是自由的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.44,0:12:14.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你拥有可以自由翱翔宇宙的翅膀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.39,0:12:17.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然搞不懂你在说什么…总之没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.77,0:12:18.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.21,0:12:20.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.40,0:12:27.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  阿珍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.77,0:12:28.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.49,0:12:33.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿珍你是中学生吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.72,0:12:36.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该不是小学生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.49,0:12:39.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.81,0:12:41.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么阿珍要用敬语呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.24,0:12:46.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我很微不足道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.60,0:12:49.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是女孩子  却用这个自称啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.48,0:12:51.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…是我的风格啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.38,0:12:54.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么阿珍流那么多汗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.90,0:12:59.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是因为…酷夏的烈日正在折磨着我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.22,0:13:02.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈  现在是冬天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.55,0:13:03.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.78,0:13:06.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会是察觉到了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.63,0:13:08.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.66,0:13:09.40,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿珍真是文静啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.80,0:13:12.57,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是因为家里教导有方…有方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.43,0:13:11.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来吉野对阿珍有兴趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.10,0:13:33.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在看我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.40,0:13:37.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们好  在做作业吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.47,0:13:38.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也加我一个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.75,0:13:39.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.18,0:13:41.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？内田呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.78,0:13:43.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和修一去买东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.58,0:13:45.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬马！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.33,0:13:46.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.12,0:13:50.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你  坐在我和吉野中间  帮我抵挡她的攻势吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.94,0:13:52.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.86,0:13:55.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从刚才她就两眼发光的盯着我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.48,0:13:59.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是人称「坚不可推」的吉野小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.02,0:14:02.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能已经怀疑了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.21,0:14:04.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁给的名号啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.65,0:14:05.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…千秋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.12,0:14:10.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着啊  不管是不是被看穿了  
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.20,0:14:12.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之不要与她为敌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.95,0:14:14.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.83,0:14:16.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.47,0:14:17.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.72,0:14:20.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  你去哪儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.51,0:14:26.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们班留的作业  很可能是明天我们班要留的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.85,0:14:29.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在留作业之前做完  这就是我的战斗方针
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.21,0:14:32.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且千秋和吉野的中间  
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.14,0:14:36.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是可以获得两侧支援的绝佳战场
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.90,0:14:39.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了  留在这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.87,0:14:42.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.91,0:14:44.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.12,0:14:46.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！别闹了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.39,0:14:51.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么阿珍你要那么慌张啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.76,0:14:54.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是女孩子的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.05,0:14:56.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪的阿珍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.35,0:15:01.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先回去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.16,0:15:09.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了…受不了了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.50,0:15:13.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是时候罢手了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.88,0:15:15.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是挺好的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.58,0:15:17.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛…是夏奈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.40,0:15:19.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我该怎么办好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.66,0:15:21.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌的年糕也会总有一天会喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.41,0:15:24.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？我喜欢吃年糕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.16,0:15:29.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎样  你不这么打扮恐怕就进不了我家门啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.55,0:15:30.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.65,0:15:33.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写完了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.33,0:15:36.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头脑好的凑在一块就是做得快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.34,0:15:39.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是觉得因为没有笨蛋在场
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.68,0:15:41.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都回去的很早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.81,0:15:44.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.18,0:15:45.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.70,0:15:49.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有事…要拜托千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.62,0:15:53.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想有所改变  像千秋那样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.76,0:15:55.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你突然在说些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.79,0:15:58.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讨厌被叫做原味酸奶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.07,0:16:02.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不喜欢吃胡萝卜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.09,0:16:03.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会错意啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.07,0:16:12.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须去买东西了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.16,0:16:17.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我变了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.09,0:16:19.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得是变了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.62,0:16:21.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪方面？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.06,0:16:23.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变得爱说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.48,0:16:26.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没觉得自己变了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.41,0:16:28.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.25,0:16:31.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  我不认为换个外号人就会变
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.98,0:16:32.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.21,0:16:36.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别那么沮丧  主要还是看自己
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.64,0:16:37.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.84,0:16:40.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是修一  也是有优点的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.96,0:16:42.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？哪方面？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.75,0:16:44.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要问哪方面嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.80,0:16:48.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非要说的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.46,0:16:49.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非要说的话…？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.16,0:16:51.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.32,0:16:54.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别急啊…你头脑不差啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.73,0:16:57.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.73,0:17:01.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你想说笨蛋才有个性吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.59,0:17:02.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.58,0:17:13.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.53,0:17:14.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.03,0:17:16.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐躺你身边你就无视啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.91,0:17:18.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才一亿日元而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.76,0:17:19.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦  听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.52,0:17:23.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我梦见千秋你吧哩吧哩的吃胡萝卜条了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.66,0:17:24.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.55,0:17:27.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后好像又吃了什么好吃的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.96,0:17:32.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊  这里刚好放着我梦见的胡萝卜条呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.97,0:17:34.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了你  一边儿去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.49,0:17:36.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  千秋  请用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.49,0:17:37.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.95,0:17:41.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不先吃了这个  也许就吃不到好东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.47,0:17:42.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.30,0:17:44.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.72,0:17:53.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋  换洗衣服我放这里了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.19,0:17:55.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  春香姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.58,0:17:58.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐姐  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.07,0:17:59.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.16,0:18:02.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是变了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.72,0:18:04.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  突然这么问
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.63,0:18:07.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天有人说我变了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.15,0:18:09.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友说的？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.46,0:18:10.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.32,0:18:12.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我想就是变了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.96,0:18:17.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和大家在一起会不知不觉受到影响的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.05,0:18:20.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗完澡就来吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.83,0:18:27.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是说对了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.59,0:18:29.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管你对不对！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.76,0:18:31.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃螃蟹啊  要把这壳…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.98,0:18:35.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对  要把壳这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.41,0:18:37.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.64,0:18:43.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊…看错了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.35,0:18:47.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为是胡萝卜条  其实是螃蟹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.69,0:18:50.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过还是不说了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.64,0:18:57.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螃蟹就是要安安静静的吃嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.14,0:19:04.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.95,0:19:06.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.82,0:19:07.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.89,0:19:09.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.60,0:19:13.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还说怎么了…奶油花居然…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.54,0:19:16.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶油花？又是预知梦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.39,0:19:17.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正你根本没做梦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.11,0:19:20.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做是做了  可我忘了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.40,0:19:23.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办才好？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.07,0:19:24.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.91,0:19:26.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋啊  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.77,0:19:28.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是在等人吐槽吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.68,0:19:31.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…什么都没看见哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.81,0:19:33.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管吗？真不管吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.95,0:19:35.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知道能忍到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.80,0:19:37.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.35,0:19:41.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们偷偷摸摸的说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.02,0:19:46.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.17,0:19:47.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.96,0:19:49.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上…好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.30,0:19:50.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好…呃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.97,0:19:52.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.01,0:19:54.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.54,0:19:57.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作业带来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.97,0:19:58.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作业…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.94,0:20:00.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到作业…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.54,0:20:04.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿珍…现在在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.07,0:20:06.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南家三姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.25,0:20:06.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,～再来一碗～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.39,0:20:11.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把领带系紧了  保坂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.61,0:20:12.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  老师
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.94,0:20:17.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇哇～春香为我做了便当哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.26,0:20:22.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么打我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.38,0:20:23.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你要抢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.38,0:20:30.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保坂啊  你不是为了让春香吃才每天做便当的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.92,0:20:33.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然一次都没送出
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.61,0:20:36.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想吃春香的便当吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.31,0:20:38.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是想让春香吃你做的便当呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.08,0:20:39.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哪个？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.84,0:20:44.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速水前辈  今天的社团活动…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.46,0:20:46.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希！作为参考我问问你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.38,0:20:49.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是吃的那方还是被吃的那方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.92,0:20:50.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.21,0:20:53.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想…应该是吃的那方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.90,0:20:54.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.56,0:20:59.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希  不要因为想脱身就乱说话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.00,0:21:02.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为他太恶心…呃  太有魄力才…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.11,0:21:06.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来你真是丢脸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.40,0:21:09.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保坂  你本该是个做任何事都拼尽全力的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.30,0:21:13.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但现在的你却迷失了自我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.11,0:21:17.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好想一想  你渴望的到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.63,0:21:19.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.16,0:21:22.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底渴望什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.25,0:21:25.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师  我到底应该怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.81,0:21:27.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把领带系好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.37,0:21:28.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  老师
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.13,0:21:34.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪你  便当都一塌糊涂了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.49,0:21:35.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么赔我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.70,0:21:38.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才踢了我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.37,0:21:39.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踢了又怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.89,0:21:40.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.77,0:21:44.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊…这就是答案啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.58,0:21:46.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是踢还是打
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.28,0:21:48.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吃还是被吃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.91,0:21:50.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是二选一的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.77,0:21:53.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我两边都要！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.93,0:21:55.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  我是保坂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.25,0:21:58.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是一塌糊涂  也照吃！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.72,0:21:59.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不给你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.50,0:23:33.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有认为喝醋就会让身体变软的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.92,0:23:36.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鱼骨沾到醋确实会变软
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.72,0:23:39.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是人骨和鱼骨可不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.24,0:23:42.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醋会在人体内分解成炭酸和水
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.50,0:23:44.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是趁早放弃这念头去做柔体运动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.26,0:23:44.97,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\an8\fad(370,0)}第10碗  「舍华求实的年纪」
